715746f-a.title: Manhattan: 166th Street (West) - Edgecombe Avenue
715746f-a.text:
461 West 166th Street, north side, between Edgecombe and Amsterdam
AVes., showing the Den Norske Frei Missions Menighed. This new brick
structure replaced a 2-story frame house that appears in Bromley's Atlas
of 1922.
April 8, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
